  "text": "Spectrophotometry was used in order to evaluate PPO enzymatic activity. Therefore, 100 µL of JeEE were added to 3 mL of catechol solution 0.07 M in PBS media 0.05 M (pH 6.0), and absorbance at 420 nm was evaluated after 10 min using a spectrophotometer (Q798U2VS, Quimis Aparelhos Científicos Ltd., São Paulo, Brasil) [CITATION_1] . PPO activity was expressed in U/mg protein.",
